{"tid":2497991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB 五大最高薪人員","createTime":"2021-04-21T00:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T00:59:46.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ebde0d17198941a29daf005bcafd9fe045c9816","tid":2497991,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T00:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i4cBV1Z3-Vo3ykdFn1ewsoC_tzY=/535x417/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TIAHFIODFRFGZGVXMSZYWKUYSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi4cBV1Z3-Vo3ykdFn1ewsoC_tzY%3D%2F535x417%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTIAHFIODFRFGZGVXMSZYWKUYSM.jpg&h=5098da16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MPVsyoH-S1QIDbFZnxbMx6HxPOU=/535x420/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A232NNK77FHUNNBHKWTWK27WFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMPVsyoH-S1QIDbFZnxbMx6HxPOU%3D%2F535x420%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA232NNK77FHUNNBHKWTWK27WFE.jpg&h=75154acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n上市公司陸續出年報，記者最八卦其中一個項目叫「董事酬金」及「最高薪人士」列表。最高薪一族，未必一定係董事局成員，亦未必最能幫公司賺錢，反而可能是手握大權，或是獲老闆「賞識」。近年被外界指節目老化、山頭林立的TVB（511），究竟誰是五大高薪成員，可由年報找線索。<br />\n<br />\n2019年五位最高薪人員，董事佔兩席，其餘三位平均每位總報酬550萬元。較大可能就是高層管理人員。當年年報上，撇除李寶安，TVB列出另外三位高層管理人員，分別是副總經理（節目及製作）杜之克、財務總監及公司秘書麥佑基，及副總經理（法律及國際業務）陳樹鴻。<br />\n<br />\n2020年年報，不計李寶安，其餘四位最高酬人士，估計亦是高層人員，平均每位收取約470萬元，相信除了杜之克、麥佑基及陳樹鴻外，尚有另外一位「手握大權」人士。最新年報裡，高層管理人員合照多了一個新名字：曾志偉。理論上，副總經理（綜藝、音樂製作及節目）曾志偉今年初先重新加入無線，不會是去年最高薪的人員，但今年極大機會成為Top 5。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210420/BC6LXXXDX5DS3BJLBY6NQS2LOM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210420%2FBC6LXXXDX5DS3BJLBY6NQS2LOM%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=6b51a811\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210420%2FBC6LXXXDX5DS3BJLBY6NQS2LOM%2F&h=95ff2775\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210420/BC6LXXXDX5DS3BJLBY6NQS2LOM/</a>"},{"pid":"450fca3da588c6950ffcece10019ed62e2d3d992","tid":2497991,"uid":269712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T00:54:59.000Z","msg":"放係娛樂台，放咩時事台呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191bad479620fe7106e4052f7768bea42edb5df4","tid":2497991,"uid":37856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T00:55:34.000Z","msg":"乜李寶安原來咁矮"},{"pid":"e6226df6b1138f3f44cee4c45ff3ff4bf44dcb37","tid":2497991,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T00:56:50.000Z","msg":"李寶安件垃圾都可以收九百萬一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5306bef7cf62fa07fa3d8b1b221d70736eb382","tid":2497991,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"191bad479620fe7106e4052f7768bea42edb5df4","tid":2497991,"uid":37856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T00:55:34.000Z","msg":"乜李寶安原來咁矮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T00:59:46.000Z","msg":"米奇拉高咗幾多個頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}